Motormaster. "What do we do, commander?" he asks, watching the bots.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Killfest stands near Motormaster, ready for battle.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

base. Despite his arrogance, he had to admit to himself that he would 
have just a bit of trouble slagging all these bots if it came to 
that, just a bit (Autofire's not that strong, he's just arrogant).
